body:
Riot KateyKhaos - &quot;This issue won&#039;t be fixed in 6.2. - we&#039;re still working on it.&quot; 

LOL so everyone who was hoping to play league this patch (who need per-side offset camera ) you can kiss your plans goodbye. Riot have decided that this bug isn&#039;t &quot;game breaking&quot; enough to be bothered to hotfix the problem asap in-fact they have decided that we can wait out the whole patch for it lol.

Riot KateyKhaos - &quot;(I&#039;m just the messenger here, so I don&#039;t have much additional info.)&quot;

So the correct department that has been informed of this bug but haven&#039;t got the time to tell everyone about this game breaking bug for the majority of players who play locked camera. Instead we are left with no knowledge or recognition of the severity of this  bug except that its being worked on for the entirety of patch 6.2 AKA its not big enough of a bug ( even though its game breaking ) for us to be bothered to do anything about it.
